with no DJ to hail us,

00:18:11.230 --> 00:18:15.640
no ads if you pay enough,
songs and playlists selected

00:18:15.640 --> 00:18:20.290
for you not by a DJ,
but by algorithms.

00:18:20.290 --> 00:18:22.470
The AIing of taste.

00:18:22.470 --> 00:18:25.550
I think this should be
part of radio studies too.

