Ramón, one of the cofounders,

01:40:05.330 --> 01:40:07.600
the only woman cofounder
of Radio KDNA,

01:40:07.600 --> 01:40:11.030
the nation's first full time
Spanish language noncommercial

01:40:11.030 --> 01:40:12.470
radio station in
the United States

01:40:12.470 --> 01:40:16.320
that was founded,
went on air in 1979.

01:40:16.320 --> 01:40:20.490
