revolutionized the ways

01:40:20.490 --> 01:40:23.120
in which we understand Spanish
language radio, particularly

01:40:23.120 --> 01:40:26.030
when it comes to intentionally
incorporating women

01:40:26.030 --> 01:40:28.380
into broadcasting as producers,

01:40:28.380 --> 01:40:31.200
