01:40:55.880 --> 01:40:59.070
Chicanos that beginning
in the 1950's migrated

01:40:59.070 --> 01:41:01.940
to the Pacific Northwest
to work in the hops,

01:41:01.940 --> 01:41:05.290
apples, cherries, asparagus.

01:41:05.290 --> 01:41:06.590
You name it, they're there.

01:41:06.590 --> 01:41:13.360
