01:51:19.850 --> 01:51:21.150
And I though uh.

01:51:21.150 --> 01:51:22.460
So, I just want to,
just give you,

01:51:22.460 --> 01:51:26.210
just to give you one example
of what we dealt with.

01:51:26.210 --> 01:51:29.520
I was invited to
speak to a religious.

01:51:29.520 --> 01:51:31.160
The denomination doesn't matter.

01:51:31.160 --> 01:51:34.900
But a religious group and one of
the questions that they asked me

01:51:34.900 --> 01:51:39.010
in this interview, they
wanted to about Radio KDNA,

01:51:39.010 --> 01:51:42.470
