higher than the animals.

01:51:45.700 --> 01:51:48.130
So, that was one of the
first questions that I dealt

01:51:48.130 --> 01:51:51.820
with when our station
first went in the air.

01:51:51.820 --> 01:51:55.360
So, it gives you an idea
of why it's so remarkable

01:51:55.360 --> 01:51:57.720
that the first Spanish language
radio station should come

01:51:57.720 --> 01:52:01.960
out of this tiny, poor town
in the State of Washington.

01:52:01.960 --> 01:52:06.040
And that it has accomplished
what it has done.

01:52:06.040 --> 01:52:12.730
In terms of one very
important issue tackling AIDS

01:52:12.730 --> 01:52:14.400
