01:52:17.860 --> 01:52:22.330
Radio KDNA took that on and did
a national program in Spanish.

01:52:22.330 --> 01:52:25.810
It did a radio drama
series in Spanish

01:52:25.810 --> 01:52:28.150
to educate the Latino community.

01:52:28.150 --> 01:52:34.220
So, that's, that's the kind of
station, you know, that it is.

