forgotten about the show,

02:58:13.390 --> 02:58:14.990
similar to my family members,
because of the reality

02:58:14.990 --> 02:58:16.290
that Haiti was not
going to be a space

02:58:16.290 --> 02:58:17.590
that we could return
to as a family.

02:58:17.590 --> 02:58:19.750
