02:59:34.950 --> 02:59:37.630
Does Columbia University own
these rights for this show?

02:59:37.630 --> 02:59:47.070
Does, do the owners or creators
of the show own the rights?

02:59:47.070 --> 02:59:51.050
Does WKCR, the radio station
that operates independently

02:59:51.050 --> 02:59:53.450
out of Columbia University
own the rights?

02:59:53.450 --> 02:59:56.310
And so, there are so
many questions in, in,

02:59:56.310 --> 03:00:03.200
